	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey, I just registered at another site, and they had a great method of dealing with spambots. There were about 8 textboxes in the registration process that it said in big letters to leave empty. If you didn't leave it empty, it would think you're a spambot. They were all in a row, so it said that spambots always fill in some of the boxes. Maybe something like that should be implemented here.

		

		</td>
